        <img src="~/Images/Thinh.jpg" class="img-thumbnail img-responsive pull-left" style="width: 150px; display: inline-block; margin: 0 30px 30px 0" />
        <p>Whether it is perfectly matching a buyer with their dream home, or negotiating for his sellers to obtain the best possible price, you can rest assure that Thinh Huynh will be making sure that any job is always done the right way. This relentless hunger for satisfying his clients combined with his contagious positive attitude makes Thinh a very popular real estate figure within the area.</p>
